snippet.title: Starboost EX early-access trailer
snippet.description:
Developer: KOEX studio
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/917990/PUNK_EX_2093
Platforms: Steam

Starboost EX is a fasted-paced Land, Air and Space shooter with more than 30+ single-player missions.

'BOOM' a ex-space engineer seeking revenge for his dead family that is killed by the 'Snakers', a extraterrestrial beings from a parallel universe of Gaia.

Join us on Discord here: https://discord.gg/EjB3QMd

Follow Starboost EX on Twitter 
https://twitter.com/starboost_ex

Like Starboost EX on Facebook: 
 https://www.facebook.com/starboostex

#indiegame #steam #scifi #shooter
